Use the standard library
This is how to count_up_to of n:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that candidate is 2

   Do this n times:
      When candidate is at most n, then:
         Remember that factors is 0
         Remember that divisor is 1

         Do this candidate times:
            When remainder of candidate and divisor is 0, then:
               Increase factors
            End when
            Increase divisor
         End do

         When factors is 2, then:
            Add result to candidate
         End when
      End when
      Increase candidate
   End do

   The answer is result
Now you know